question: What is the number of endangered dolphin which was found along the Hastinapur Wildlife Sanctuary and Narora Ramsar site after conducting annual Ganges river dolphin census 2019
explanation: A total number of 36 endangered (IUCN Red data) dolphin was found long the Hastinapur Wildlife Sanctuary and Narora Ramsar site after conducting annual Ganges river dolphin census 2019. In the year 2018, it was 33.
